{
  "texts": [
    "In the realm of catalyst-related tasks, LLM's performance can be significantly enhanced by employing prompt engineering (PE) which can steer LLMs toward generating precise and pertinent information.",
    "Although LLMs, including fine-tuned LLMs, can answer general questions, their knowledge depth, accuracy and timeliness are limited in vertical domain filed.",
    "To solve this problem, we use vector databases to enhance the reasoning ability of LLMs in vertical domains.",
    "Vector databases can transform literature and data into vector representations by embedding vectors.",
    "Sci-BERT 31 was used as embedding model for construct the vector database."
  ]
}